cat << EOF

dwm hotkeys
=================

alt +
-----------------

    y           terminal (that would be z on mac)
    w           iceweasel
    x           thunar
    p           dmenu 
    b           hide statusbar
    return      put active window to main view
    #           jump to workspace #
    h/l         vertical resize
    j/k         jump around windows
    i/d         include more windows into master-area
    f/m/t       modes (floating, monocle, tiling)
    0           show all tags

    a           runs custom command centerWindow (depends on xrandr and xdotool)

shift + alt
-----------------

    c           close window
    q           close dwm
    return      terminal
    #           move active window to workspace #
    0           tag to all workspaces
    space       terminal

mice
-----------------

    mod + lmb   move   (floating mode)
    mod + rmb   resize (floating mode)

toggle float mode
-----------------

    alt + shift + space or
    alt + middle mouse

note: workspaces are actually tags, mkay.

EOF
